1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[English subtitles are available]

2
00:01:32,100 --> 00:01:36,780
[Eternal Brotherhood 1]

3
00:01:39,289 --> 00:01:42,820
[Episode 16]

4
00:02:01,110 --> 00:02:01,570
My Lord.

5
00:02:02,720 --> 00:02:03,520
What's wrong?

6
00:02:03,780 --> 00:02:05,830
Si Yilin's army still gave an order to pursue the enemy.

7
00:02:05,830 --> 00:02:06,990
Now they've crossed Chishuitan

8
00:02:06,990 --> 00:02:08,419
and entered the central region of Yuntai.

9
00:02:08,419 --> 00:02:10,389
They ignored the military order from the Ministry of War.

10
00:02:10,389 --> 00:02:12,990
Deputy Commander Luo Bo has been handed over to the Ministry of Military and Legal Affairs.

11
00:02:12,990 --> 00:02:13,710
Okay.

12
00:02:14,460 --> 00:02:17,410
Tell Di Lin to punish him severely.

13
00:02:18,270 --> 00:02:18,670
Yes.

14
00:02:20,430 --> 00:02:21,230
Mr. Xiu.

15
00:02:22,150 --> 00:02:24,079
If you think it's a dilemma for you,

16
00:02:24,380 --> 00:02:25,380
I can understand.

17
00:02:25,480 --> 00:02:27,180
Lord Luo has done me a great favor.

18
00:02:27,180 --> 00:02:28,300
I will do my best.

19
00:02:28,950 --> 00:02:30,480
Luo Bo didn't misjudge you.

20
00:02:31,100 --> 00:02:33,700
Lord Ge Yingxing didn't misjudge you, either.

21
00:02:37,390 --> 00:02:38,520
Speaking of Lord Ge,

22
00:02:38,900 --> 00:02:40,950
there's one thing I've been unable to understand.

23
00:02:40,950 --> 00:02:41,480
Go ahead.

24
00:02:43,030 --> 00:02:47,030
Why did Lord Ge take the road that was within the Lin Family's territory?

25
00:02:48,350 --> 00:02:50,340
The Imperial Capital was in danger at that time.

26
00:02:50,340 --> 00:02:54,540
The Yuanzhou Army was restrained by the North Clan and couldn't fight back.

27
00:02:54,550 --> 00:02:56,079
However, time was limited.

28
00:02:56,510 --> 00:02:58,680
Lord Ge made a detour in the Lin Family's area

29
00:02:58,680 --> 00:03:01,080
in order to ask Master Zuo Jiaming for help.

30
00:03:06,780 --> 00:03:08,710
Before Lord Ge died, he told me that

31
00:03:09,050 --> 00:03:12,430
he was worried that no one could restrain Yang Minghua after his death.

32
00:03:12,430 --> 00:03:15,160
He said if it really happened one day,

33
00:03:15,710 --> 00:03:18,070
I should give this box to Zichuan Xiu,

34
00:03:18,900 --> 00:03:21,500
and tell Zichuan Xiu to find the owner of the box

35
00:03:21,880 --> 00:03:23,829
in order to ask him to eliminate Yang Minghua.

36
00:03:23,829 --> 00:03:25,430
That's what Lord Ge said.

37
00:03:25,910 --> 00:03:28,960
So Master Zuo Jiaming really exists?

38
00:03:33,110 --> 00:03:35,770
Rumour has it that every generation of every family

39
00:03:35,770 --> 00:03:38,510
has a powerful man who is known as the top martial arts master.

40
00:03:38,510 --> 00:03:40,170
But among these powerful men,

41
00:03:40,370 --> 00:03:42,040
only one of them is recognized by

42
00:03:42,040 --> 00:03:43,110
the whole continent,

43
00:03:43,110 --> 00:03:45,770
namely, Master Zuo Jiaming from the Lin Family.

44
00:03:46,300 --> 00:03:48,630
It is said that he's over 300 years old now.

45
00:03:48,760 --> 00:03:50,870
I had thought that it was just a legend.

46
00:03:50,870 --> 00:03:53,960
Master Zuo Jiaming was born in the Guangming Empire.

47
00:03:54,630 --> 00:03:56,790
When he was 21, he was appointed

48
00:03:56,810 --> 00:04:00,940
as the State Preceptor by Lin Jianyi, the emperor of the Guangming Empire.

49
00:04:01,310 --> 00:04:02,710
He once used his own power

50
00:04:03,140 --> 00:04:05,950
to repel the North Clan's army consisting of 100,000 soldiers,

51
00:04:05,950 --> 00:04:07,350
and killed 3,000 people.

52
00:04:08,510 --> 00:04:10,870
Later, he acknowledged Lin Jianyi's daughter,

53
00:04:10,870 --> 00:04:12,780
Lin Fengxi, as the head of the family.

54
00:04:12,780 --> 00:04:15,840
He protected the Lin Family for several hundred years.

55
00:04:22,670 --> 00:04:24,240
I will keep it well.

56
00:04:27,000 --> 00:04:30,640
However, it shouldn't be given to me so early.

57
00:04:40,450 --> 00:04:44,140
By the way, did you guys see Lei Hong in Yuanzhou?

58
00:04:44,990 --> 00:04:47,940
We did fight with Lei Hong's rebel army several times.

59
00:04:47,940 --> 00:04:50,110
But we didn't see him in person all the time.

60
00:04:50,110 --> 00:04:51,110
He was so cunning.

61
00:04:54,790 --> 00:04:56,190
No matter where he hides,

62
00:04:56,590 --> 00:04:58,710
I'll find him eventually.

63
00:05:01,300 --> 00:05:02,900
Let's not talk about this now.

64
00:05:02,900 --> 00:05:04,430
The most important thing now

65
00:05:04,430 --> 00:05:06,110
is Lord Luo's problem.

66
00:05:09,680 --> 00:05:15,410
In fact, the most suitable person is my Big Brother, Di Lin.

67
00:05:17,340 --> 00:05:19,460
I shouldn't have been so stubborn.

68
00:05:20,860 --> 00:05:22,940
Now I have to beg him.

69
00:05:23,750 --> 00:05:27,040
[Di's Mansion]

70
00:05:38,650 --> 00:05:41,720
What? You lost your own statue,

71
00:05:41,760 --> 00:05:43,360
so you want to take mine away?

72
00:05:44,200 --> 00:05:45,409
It's just a statue.

73
00:05:45,680 --> 00:05:48,680
If Xiu likes it, can you really refuse to give it to him?

74
00:05:48,920 --> 00:05:50,860
I even want to take away all the objects

75
00:05:50,860 --> 00:05:52,010
in your study room.

76
00:05:52,170 --> 00:05:55,700
Okay. Take them away if you're strong enough to carry them away.

77
00:05:59,080 --> 00:06:01,190
Xiujia, go get some rest first,

78
00:06:01,910 --> 00:06:05,110
in case someone should pretend to be drunk later after taking just a sip of wine,

79
00:06:05,110 --> 00:06:06,770
and take advantage of my wife.

80
00:06:06,810 --> 00:06:09,750
I haven't seen your Big Brother be so happy for a long time.

81
00:06:09,750 --> 00:06:10,550
You guys talk.

82
00:06:18,070 --> 00:06:18,730
Have a seat.

83
00:06:27,870 --> 00:06:29,310
Are you here for Luo Bo?

84
00:06:31,830 --> 00:06:32,690
Can he be saved?

85
00:06:33,170 --> 00:06:34,100
I'll do my best.

86
00:06:34,120 --> 00:06:34,670
Really?

87
00:06:37,070 --> 00:06:39,830
It seems that people can't tell lies all their lives.

88
00:06:39,830 --> 00:06:41,150
I only lied to you once.

89
00:06:41,890 --> 00:06:44,490
I'm afraid you'll hate me all your life, right?

90
00:06:52,310 --> 00:06:54,970
Don't you need my help to solve your own problem?

91
00:06:55,310 --> 00:06:56,790
What problem can I have?

92
00:06:59,460 --> 00:07:01,300
The Reserve Service Troops heading for Yuanzhou

93
00:07:01,300 --> 00:07:02,470
have long departed.

94
00:07:03,170 --> 00:07:06,520
But you were the only one who didn't receive the transfer order.

95
00:07:06,520 --> 00:07:08,160
That means Lord Chieftain

96
00:07:08,270 --> 00:07:11,130
wants to turn you into a useless pawn deliberately.

97
00:07:15,350 --> 00:07:17,010
It's good to be a useless pawn.

98
00:07:17,620 --> 00:07:20,260
A useless pawn can enjoy a leisure life.

99
00:07:22,550 --> 00:07:25,500
Xiu, that day, I...

100
00:07:25,530 --> 00:07:28,720
Big Brother, I understand.

101
00:07:29,630 --> 00:07:31,030
You did it for my own good.

102
00:07:31,830 --> 00:07:33,230
I still let you down in the end.

103
00:07:33,230 --> 00:07:35,830
I'm happy that you called me Big Brother again.

104
00:07:37,790 --> 00:07:38,250
Come on.

105
00:07:40,710 --> 00:07:41,440
Here you are.

106
00:07:48,550 --> 00:07:50,750
It's good to be in the Imperial Capital.

107
00:07:50,750 --> 00:07:53,280
Now Luo Minghai is determined to deal with me.

108
00:07:53,350 --> 00:07:56,080
Now I'm doing everything I can to protect myself.

109
00:07:56,430 --> 00:07:58,710
Though I'm confident that I won't lose to him,

110
00:07:58,710 --> 00:08:02,110
things are unpredictable. Who knows what the result will be?

111
00:08:02,180 --> 00:08:06,270
If anything wrong happens to me,

112
00:08:07,180 --> 00:08:08,710
please take care of Xiujia.

113
00:08:10,830 --> 00:08:11,560
Big Brother.

114
00:08:16,490 --> 00:08:19,050
Don't worry. I promise you that

115
00:08:20,350 --> 00:08:21,920
as long as I'm alive,

116
00:08:22,670 --> 00:08:26,050
I won't let your wife get hurt.

117
00:08:30,340 --> 00:08:31,400
Forget what I said.

118
00:08:40,059 --> 00:08:40,539
My Lord.

119
00:08:42,510 --> 00:08:44,310
Di Lin sentenced Luo Bo to death.

120
00:08:45,190 --> 00:08:45,790
What?

121
00:08:48,850 --> 00:08:50,650
According to the law of Zichuan,

122
00:08:51,630 --> 00:08:54,990
those who disregard military orders and cause major losses

123
00:08:55,150 --> 00:08:58,080
should be removed from their posts and put into jail.

124
00:08:58,500 --> 00:09:01,100
Luo Bo shouldn't have been sentenced to death.

125
00:09:01,390 --> 00:09:03,110
Di Lin has the nickname of Executioner.

126
00:09:03,110 --> 00:09:05,790
It's not out of expectation that he did this.

127
00:09:14,430 --> 00:09:18,360
No. When Yang Minghua was still an influential minister,

128
00:09:18,940 --> 00:09:22,030
Di Lin already wanted to interfere in Yuanzhou's affairs.

129
00:09:22,030 --> 00:09:24,720
This time, he took the chance to punish Luo Bo.

130
00:09:25,570 --> 00:09:29,570
I think his purpose is to take over Yuanzhou's deployment in the future.

131
00:09:29,790 --> 00:09:31,050
My Lord, you think that

132
00:09:31,270 --> 00:09:34,070
Di Lin has an ulterior motive for punishing Luo Bo?

133
00:09:34,150 --> 00:09:36,410
We can't make this conclusion so easily.

134
00:09:36,870 --> 00:09:40,000
We still need to ask for Lord Chieftain's instructions.

135
00:09:41,150 --> 00:09:42,650
Just as you expected,

136
00:09:43,150 --> 00:09:46,550
since you want to kill Luo Bo, he's going to intercede for him.

137
00:09:47,480 --> 00:09:50,140
Luo Minghai is an honest and diligent official.

138
00:09:51,250 --> 00:09:54,020
But he has been working for Yang Minghua for so long that he has become adept at scheming.

139
00:09:54,020 --> 00:09:56,350
Besides, he's determined to deal with me.

140
00:09:57,550 --> 00:09:59,810
A wise man can be ruined by his own wisdom.

141
00:10:00,240 --> 00:10:03,940
In this way, Second Brother should be happy.

142
00:10:09,870 --> 00:10:10,340
My Lord.

143
00:10:13,730 --> 00:10:15,460
Princess Ning wants to see you.

144
00:10:19,390 --> 00:10:20,670
Ning

145
00:10:21,020 --> 00:10:23,830
hasn't come to see me for five or six days.

146
00:10:24,230 --> 00:10:26,560
What's wrong today? She has thought of me?

147
00:10:28,230 --> 00:10:29,030
Let her in.

148
00:10:30,620 --> 00:10:32,840
Well, Her Highness...

149
00:10:33,440 --> 00:10:34,240
What's wrong?

150
00:10:38,430 --> 00:10:41,710
Ning, why are you kneeling?

151
00:10:41,990 --> 00:10:43,270
Come on. Stand up.

152
00:10:43,790 --> 00:10:47,550
Uncle, I have something to say.

153
00:10:47,550 --> 00:10:50,070
But you'll definitely be angry after you hear it.

154
00:10:50,070 --> 00:10:51,430
So I'd better go on kneeling.

155
00:10:51,430 --> 00:10:52,590
What are you talking about?

156
00:10:52,590 --> 00:10:54,750
After I get angry, I'll be even angrier if you go on kneeling.

157
00:10:54,750 --> 00:10:56,420
Stand up. Just tell me what you want to say. Come on.

158
00:10:56,420 --> 00:10:57,880
Uncle, listen to me first.

159
00:10:58,310 --> 00:10:59,680
When my father was alive,

160
00:10:59,680 --> 00:11:00,830
he once told me that

161
00:11:00,900 --> 00:11:02,530
I had been weak in childhood.

162
00:11:02,780 --> 00:11:05,910
I even almost died from a serious disease when I was a kid.

163
00:11:06,140 --> 00:11:08,320
A doctor prescribed a folk prescription.

164
00:11:08,320 --> 00:11:12,380
He said there was a kind of Phoenix Bee in the wilderness of the North Clan.

165
00:11:12,510 --> 00:11:14,010
It chirped like a phoenix,

166
00:11:14,430 --> 00:11:16,960
and its honey could be used to cure my disease.

167
00:11:17,300 --> 00:11:20,500
You sneaked into the North Clan to find and get this honey.

168
00:11:23,860 --> 00:11:25,940
This is the Phoenix Bee honey found by you.

169
00:11:25,940 --> 00:11:27,180
It saved my life.

170
00:11:28,180 --> 00:11:30,150
Because of it, I've remained healthy until now.

171
00:11:30,150 --> 00:11:32,480
Therefore, I've been very grateful to you

172
00:11:32,590 --> 00:11:34,930
since I became a sensible child.

173
00:11:35,270 --> 00:11:37,670
It is indeed hard to find this kind of honey.

174
00:11:37,940 --> 00:11:41,150
But as long as we manage to open all kinds of channels,

175
00:11:41,610 --> 00:11:43,610
there will be such honey every year.

176
00:11:43,710 --> 00:11:45,510
And this Glittering Cloak, too.

177
00:11:47,040 --> 00:11:50,300
When I was ten years old, the officials came to congratulate me.

178
00:11:50,300 --> 00:11:51,470
You made this for me.

179
00:11:52,270 --> 00:11:54,150
At that time, my father said I was just a kid,

180
00:11:54,150 --> 00:11:55,890
so the adults shouldn't spoil me too much.

181
00:11:55,890 --> 00:11:59,210
But you said I was the most beautiful princess in Zichuan,

182
00:11:59,550 --> 00:12:00,830
so only the most gorgeous clothes

183
00:12:00,830 --> 00:12:02,070
could match me.

184
00:12:02,620 --> 00:12:06,020
Uncle, you've been doting on me and loving me since I was a kid.

185
00:12:06,810 --> 00:12:08,410
After my father passed away,

186
00:12:08,710 --> 00:12:11,590
your love for me has only increased without decreasing.

187
00:12:11,590 --> 00:12:13,050
No matter what I asked for,

188
00:12:13,710 --> 00:12:14,750
you never said no.

189
00:12:16,790 --> 00:12:17,390
Ning,

190
00:12:17,600 --> 00:12:19,660
what on earth do you want to say today?

191
00:12:23,190 --> 00:12:25,390
I have another request for you, Uncle.

192
00:12:27,350 --> 00:12:29,460
Please grant me a marriage. I want to marry...

193
00:12:29,460 --> 00:12:30,410
Stop saying it.

194
00:12:30,990 --> 00:12:33,950
Ning, I dote on you and love you,

195
00:12:35,750 --> 00:12:37,970
not only because you're my elder brother's daughter

196
00:12:37,970 --> 00:12:38,900
and my niece.

197
00:12:39,120 --> 00:12:40,180
More importantly,

198
00:12:40,350 --> 00:12:42,910
the reason is that you're the princess of the Zichuan Family.

199
00:12:42,910 --> 00:12:44,800
Thus, you must be careful with

200
00:12:45,520 --> 00:12:46,910
your words and actions.

201
00:12:47,260 --> 00:12:48,940
You can't talk willfully.

202
00:12:49,510 --> 00:12:51,230
Uncle, I'm not wilful.

203
00:12:51,510 --> 00:12:52,910
I've thought it through.

204
00:12:54,140 --> 00:12:55,750
Uncle, you know what?

205
00:12:55,990 --> 00:12:59,650
I was born in an imperial family, and I've lived a prosperous life.

206
00:12:59,940 --> 00:13:01,250
Everyone is nice to me.

207
00:13:03,180 --> 00:13:06,620
People all dote on me so much that

208
00:13:07,560 --> 00:13:09,620
they always protect me from any harm.

209
00:13:10,630 --> 00:13:12,030
Everyone takes care of me

210
00:13:12,060 --> 00:13:15,350
like looking after the flowers in the greenhouse.

211
00:13:16,350 --> 00:13:19,180
But people are afraid of me, too.

212
00:13:19,630 --> 00:13:20,560
Only Xiu

213
00:13:20,590 --> 00:13:22,340
doesn't regard me as the Princess of Zichuan.

214
00:13:22,340 --> 00:13:24,380
He really treats me as Zichuan Ning.

215
00:13:26,070 --> 00:13:27,070
So, Uncle,

216
00:13:28,240 --> 00:13:30,100
I just want to be myself this time.

217
00:13:31,240 --> 00:13:32,660
I want to be with Xiu.

218
00:13:32,660 --> 00:13:34,920
Please give us your blessings, will you?

219
00:13:35,510 --> 00:13:38,170
How does Zichuan Xiu deserve to be your husband?

220
00:13:38,230 --> 00:13:40,400
He's just a deputy commander,

221
00:13:40,430 --> 00:13:41,950
and he's even in the Reserve Service Troops.

222
00:13:41,950 --> 00:13:43,110
Who are you?

223
00:13:43,790 --> 00:13:47,120
You're the princess of the Zichuan Family. You're the heir.

224
00:13:47,390 --> 00:13:50,240
How could you kneel in front of me

225
00:13:50,270 --> 00:13:53,110
and beg me to let you marry him?

226
00:13:53,390 --> 00:13:54,430
I don't care about all these things.

227
00:13:54,430 --> 00:13:56,470
I only care about Xiu.

228
00:13:56,720 --> 00:13:57,710
As long as I can be with him,

229
00:13:57,710 --> 00:13:58,990
I can give up anything.

230
00:13:59,020 --> 00:14:00,550
I can even give up my identity as a princess.

231
00:14:00,550 --> 00:14:01,220
Nonsense!

232
00:14:01,910 --> 00:14:04,310
You're just talking nonsense, aren't you?

233
00:14:09,790 --> 00:14:11,590
You're the princess of the Zichuan Family.

234
00:14:11,590 --> 00:14:12,840
You keep pestering that brat

235
00:14:12,840 --> 00:14:13,990
all day long.

236
00:14:14,030 --> 00:14:15,470
What's the point of that?

237
00:14:16,040 --> 00:14:18,460
Right. It's my fault.

238
00:14:18,790 --> 00:14:20,950
I didn't educate you well.

239
00:14:21,210 --> 00:14:23,090
It's all my fault.

240
00:14:25,350 --> 00:14:27,400
Uncle, that's not what I meant.

241
00:14:27,610 --> 00:14:29,190
I didn't forget my own responsibilities.

242
00:14:29,190 --> 00:14:30,750
I mean...

243
00:14:31,710 --> 00:14:34,920
Ning, Xiu has his strengths.

244
00:14:35,200 --> 00:14:37,790
I can understand his position in your heart.

245
00:14:38,430 --> 00:14:41,110
But you have to think about it.

246
00:14:41,670 --> 00:14:42,870
If you do this for him,

247
00:14:43,110 --> 00:14:45,130
what will happen to the Zichuan Family in the future?

248
00:14:45,130 --> 00:14:47,270
What will happen to the Zichuan Clan in the future?

249
00:14:47,270 --> 00:14:51,270
What will happen to the tens of millions of people of the Zichuan Family?

250
00:14:53,300 --> 00:14:54,750
You're 18 years old now.

251
00:14:55,870 --> 00:14:58,030
You can't be like a kid anymore.

252
00:14:59,820 --> 00:15:01,190
Just think about it.

253
00:15:21,270 --> 00:15:22,750
Tell the Ministry of War

254
00:15:23,470 --> 00:15:28,000
to order Zichuan Xiu to lead the Xiu Battalion to leave for Yuanzhou immediately.

255
00:15:29,360 --> 00:15:33,160
My Lord, which province should he go to specifically?

256
00:15:34,000 --> 00:15:35,480
Find a place in Yuanzhou.

257
00:15:36,330 --> 00:15:38,680
The farther away from the Imperial Capital, the better.

258
00:15:38,680 --> 00:15:39,280
Go at once.

259
00:15:40,610 --> 00:15:41,610
Yes, My Lord.

260
00:15:49,820 --> 00:15:50,500
Brother.

261
00:15:53,190 --> 00:15:54,830
I'll deal with

262
00:15:56,710 --> 00:15:58,350
Ning's matters well.

263
00:16:00,680 --> 00:16:04,750
I won't let anyone disturb Ning.

264
00:16:05,440 --> 00:16:07,100
Please don't worry, Brother.

