00:32:34,910 --> 00:32:35,710
Lord Si.

528
00:32:35,990 --> 00:32:38,830
I've long heard that our Border Appeasement Army is brave and fearless.

529
00:32:38,830 --> 00:32:41,310
We can finally have a rest after you've arrived here.

530
00:32:41,310 --> 00:32:42,470
It's just a rumor.

531
00:32:42,960 --> 00:32:45,190
Compared with the buddies of the Palace Guards,

532
00:32:45,190 --> 00:32:48,850
the Border Appeasement Army is really living a comfortable life.

533
00:32:52,790 --> 00:32:55,710
We used to be the second unit to defend against the Lin Family.

534
00:32:55,710 --> 00:32:58,640
But since we're here, we can't come here for nothing.

535
00:33:00,190 --> 00:33:02,230
This is the Weiyu Forest.

536
00:33:03,100 --> 00:33:05,630
The main force of the rebel army is in the east.

537
00:33:05,870 --> 00:33:08,530
And this area is the defence area of your troops.

538
00:33:08,750 --> 00:33:09,590
My troops

539
00:33:11,190 --> 00:33:14,160
are going to take defensive measures in this zone

540
00:33:14,390 --> 00:33:17,670
in order to fight against the rebel army with your troops.

541
00:33:18,950 --> 00:33:20,270
The Border Appeasement Army's defensive deployment

542
00:33:20,270 --> 00:33:22,710
is nearly all set up behind the Palace Guards' defensive deployment.

543
00:33:22,710 --> 00:33:23,860
This is considered as fighting side by side?

544
00:33:23,860 --> 00:33:25,920
Your troops are more familiar with this place.

545
00:33:25,920 --> 00:33:27,400
We still need to get adapted to it.

546
00:33:27,400 --> 00:33:29,120
Let's all try to understand each other.

547
00:33:29,120 --> 00:33:30,870
Okay. Got it.

548
00:33:31,430 --> 00:33:32,510
It's getting late.

549
00:33:33,030 --> 00:33:34,610
We had a long trip today.

550
00:33:35,030 --> 00:33:37,630
Let's talk about the rest of the plan tomorrow.

551
00:33:55,350 --> 00:33:56,230
Ning.

552
00:33:57,270 --> 00:33:58,920
Just now, I saw a servant

553
00:33:58,950 --> 00:34:00,580
sneak into your room.

554
00:34:01,350 --> 00:34:02,310
Did you see him?

555
00:34:04,200 --> 00:34:06,970
No, I think I've caught a cold.

556
00:34:07,270 --> 00:34:10,070
I don't even have the strength to get out of bed.

557
00:34:10,070 --> 00:34:11,130
Don't come near me.

558
00:34:11,270 --> 00:34:12,800
I'm afraid I'll infect you.

559
00:34:18,830 --> 00:34:20,790
Okay. I got it.

560
00:34:23,850 --> 00:34:24,290
You...

561
00:34:26,469 --> 00:34:27,400
Are you leaving?

562
00:34:27,840 --> 00:34:30,790
No. I'm not feeling well, right?

563
00:34:30,820 --> 00:34:32,239
I thought it was too stuffy,

564
00:34:32,239 --> 00:34:34,100
so I needed to go out to take a walk.

565
00:34:36,909 --> 00:34:38,040
The map of Yuanzhou.

566
00:34:39,949 --> 00:34:41,679
Can you take a walk to Yuanzhou?

567
00:34:41,920 --> 00:34:44,270
Ka Dan, what you said...

568
00:34:45,370 --> 00:34:45,920
No.

569
00:34:46,350 --> 00:34:48,760
My own words have made me figure it out.

570
00:34:50,449 --> 00:34:53,179
I should bear both the happiness and pain myself.

571
00:34:56,239 --> 00:34:59,360
I regret that I didn't ask him clearly that day.

572
00:34:59,680 --> 00:35:01,280
He probably hasn't gone far.

573
00:35:01,800 --> 00:35:03,280
It's not too late for me to set off now.

574
00:35:03,280 --> 00:35:04,420
I must ask him to give me

575
00:35:04,420 --> 00:35:05,500
a clear answer.

576
00:35:08,500 --> 00:35:10,700
Now it's not the time to ask him clearly.

577
00:35:11,360 --> 00:35:13,160
You can wait for him to come back.

578
00:35:14,500 --> 00:35:16,710
Ka Dan, the person I like

579
00:35:17,070 --> 00:35:18,870
doesn't allow me to wait for him.

580
00:35:20,830 --> 00:35:23,060
What if he really doesn't come back?

581
00:35:23,710 --> 00:35:26,860
What if he falls in love with someone else,

582
00:35:28,000 --> 00:35:30,400
gets married and has children in Yuanzhou?

583
00:35:30,490 --> 00:35:32,380
What if he still doesn't come back

584
00:35:32,570 --> 00:35:34,250
as I keep waiting for him?

585
00:35:35,230 --> 00:35:36,180
But Ning,

586
00:35:36,910 --> 00:35:39,190
Yuanzhou is not like the Imperial Capital.

587
00:35:39,190 --> 00:35:41,110
You're used to living in a prosperous city,

588
00:35:41,110 --> 00:35:43,640
and you can't imagine the environment there.

589
00:35:46,230 --> 00:35:48,190
I was captured in Yuanzhou.

590
00:35:48,470 --> 00:35:49,880
The wilderness and corpses there

591
00:35:49,880 --> 00:35:52,110
are still lingering in my mind.

592
00:35:52,400 --> 00:35:53,950
The refugees who were driven crazy by the war,

593
00:35:53,950 --> 00:35:55,190
the soldiers who lacked food,

594
00:35:55,190 --> 00:35:57,150
and the people from Yuanzhou who were in a desperate situation.

595
00:35:57,150 --> 00:35:58,550
Branches, hoes,

596
00:35:58,630 --> 00:35:59,700
and even stones on the roadside

597
00:35:59,700 --> 00:36:01,760
could be their life-saving weapons.

598
00:36:01,790 --> 00:36:04,220
In order to survive, they would kill anyone.

599
00:36:04,220 --> 00:36:04,850
I know.

600
00:36:04,870 --> 00:36:05,790
You don't know!

601
00:36:07,260 --> 00:36:08,140
You don't know.

602
00:36:08,550 --> 00:36:10,750
You are the heir of the Zichuan Family.

603
00:36:10,830 --> 00:36:13,650
Your safety affects the entire country of Zichuan

604
00:36:14,230 --> 00:36:16,190
and even the situation of the war.

605
00:36:16,510 --> 00:36:18,110
Though I'm the heir, so what?

606
00:36:20,100 --> 00:36:22,630
I still can't keep the person I love by my side.

607
00:36:25,360 --> 00:36:27,620
I shouldn't have said those words to you.

608
00:36:29,130 --> 00:36:30,330
No, Ka Dan.

609
00:36:32,560 --> 00:36:34,560
I'm grateful for what you said to me.

610
00:36:34,790 --> 00:36:35,990
If it weren't for you,

611
00:36:36,600 --> 00:36:39,330
now I would still be a fool who could only feel sad.

612
00:36:40,320 --> 00:36:41,450
I've made up my mind.

613
00:36:41,640 --> 00:36:43,460
I must go to Yuanzhou.

614
00:36:45,310 --> 00:36:47,430
Your Highness! Your Highness!

615
00:36:48,780 --> 00:36:50,080
What should we do?

616
00:36:50,100 --> 00:36:51,150
No, no, no.

617
00:36:58,930 --> 00:37:01,980
Princess Ning has caught a cold because she indulged in having fun.

618
00:37:01,980 --> 00:37:03,840
Butler, please send for a doctor.

619
00:37:04,060 --> 00:37:05,040
Okay.

620
00:37:25,750 --> 00:37:27,430
I knew you would help me.

621
00:37:28,070 --> 00:37:30,140
I can't get off the pirate ship now, can I?

622
00:37:30,140 --> 00:37:31,220
No, you can't.

623
00:37:33,700 --> 00:37:35,970
Currently, the news that I have a cold

624
00:37:36,000 --> 00:37:37,130
has been spread out.

625
00:37:38,030 --> 00:37:39,910
During my trip to Yuanzhou,

626
00:37:40,850 --> 00:37:43,120
just say that Princess Ning

627
00:37:43,180 --> 00:37:44,990
has been infected with plague, which is infectious,

628
00:37:44,990 --> 00:37:47,520
so it's not appropriate for her to see anyone.

629
00:37:48,640 --> 00:37:51,360
However, there is a war now.

630
00:37:51,630 --> 00:37:53,150
When soldiers check people who enter or leave the Imperial Capital,

631
00:37:53,150 --> 00:37:55,210
they'll definitely be very careful.

632
00:37:55,430 --> 00:37:58,430
Have you thought about how to get out of the city?

633
00:37:58,670 --> 00:38:00,470
I thought of someone from somewhere.

634
00:38:00,470 --> 00:38:03,730
The soldiers guarding the city gate won't dare to stop her.

635
00:38:06,270 --> 00:38:07,820
The business in the restaurant has been very good recently.

636
00:38:07,820 --> 00:38:10,150
The clerk went to replenish stocks again.

637
00:38:11,110 --> 00:38:12,640
Show me the passing permit.

638
00:38:17,470 --> 00:38:19,890
Wang Dazhuang.

639
00:38:22,910 --> 00:38:23,710
What's wrong?

640
00:38:24,130 --> 00:38:25,460
He's a clerk from Lord Di Lin's restaurant.

641
00:38:25,460 --> 00:38:27,260
How dare you call him by his name?

642
00:38:31,790 --> 00:38:32,830
Mr. Dazhuang, please.

643
00:38:32,830 --> 00:38:36,030
Give my regards to Lord Di Lin for me when there's a chance.

644
00:38:36,130 --> 00:38:38,190
There's no need to give regards to me.

645
00:38:38,950 --> 00:38:40,480
Are you doing your job well?

646
00:38:40,950 --> 00:38:41,830
Lord Di Lin.

647
00:38:43,230 --> 00:38:45,560
There were 572 people passing the city gate today.

648
00:38:45,560 --> 00:38:47,510
We all searched them one by one.

649
00:38:47,790 --> 00:38:50,110
Only after we confirmed their identities did we dare to let them pass the gate.

650
00:38:50,110 --> 00:38:52,390
This is a clerk from the Jintai Restaurant, isn't he?

651
00:38:52,390 --> 00:38:53,790
We definitely trust him.

652
00:38:58,310 --> 00:39:00,510
Are you a new clerk recruited by Xiujia?

653
00:39:02,400 --> 00:39:05,600
You can't even recognize the new clerk in our restaurant.

654
00:39:05,880 --> 00:39:08,540
It shows that you rarely come to our restaurant.

655
00:39:08,580 --> 00:39:09,510
Why are you here?

656
00:39:10,650 --> 00:39:11,580
Is it beautiful?

657
00:39:11,790 --> 00:39:15,870
Yes, it's called, "I could see her hands after her sleeves were rolled up.

658
00:39:15,890 --> 00:39:18,690
There were golden bracelets on her white wrists."

659
00:39:19,310 --> 00:39:21,710
Stop looking at us. Get out of the city at once.

660
00:39:21,710 --> 00:39:24,110
You won't be able to get fresh Baishui Fish if you don't hurry up.

661
00:39:24,110 --> 00:39:24,590
Yes.

662
00:39:29,390 --> 00:39:30,990
You're still looking at him?

663
00:39:31,070 --> 00:39:33,070
It's late now. Why don't you go home?

664
00:39:33,110 --> 00:39:34,330
I've already made some soup.

665
00:39:34,330 --> 00:39:36,590
Okay. I need to talk to Ge Qing about something.

666
00:39:36,590 --> 00:39:37,590
I'll be back soon.

667
00:39:42,310 --> 00:39:43,910
It was really Princess Ning.

668
00:39:44,110 --> 00:39:45,590
But she went out

669
00:39:45,610 --> 00:39:47,590
in the name of our Jintai Restaurant just like that.

670
00:39:47,590 --> 00:39:48,950
Is it really okay?

671
00:39:51,420 --> 00:39:53,300
My husband has never been considerate

672
00:39:53,300 --> 00:39:54,780
towards such things.

673
00:39:55,710 --> 00:39:57,770
Princess Ning is just being playful.

674
00:39:57,910 --> 00:39:59,840
She will be back in a couple of days.

675
00:40:19,860 --> 00:40:20,430
Zhui.

676
00:40:20,830 --> 00:40:23,090
I usually feed you with such good fodder.

677
00:40:23,420 --> 00:40:25,280
You must help me catch up with Xiu.

678
00:40:34,180 --> 00:40:34,710
Lord Xiu.

679
00:40:35,150 --> 00:40:36,610
Thanks for your hard work.

680
00:40:36,990 --> 00:40:37,520
Lord Xiu.

681
00:40:38,270 --> 00:40:38,800
Lord Xiu.

682
00:40:39,470 --> 00:40:39,930
Thanks for your hard work.

683
00:40:39,930 --> 00:40:40,460
Lord Xiu.

684
00:40:41,860 --> 00:40:42,940
It smells so good.

685
00:40:44,510 --> 00:40:44,970
My Lord!

686
00:40:45,680 --> 00:40:46,410
You are back.

687
00:40:47,230 --> 00:40:49,550
My Lord, we are back.

688
00:40:51,910 --> 00:40:52,970
Put your hand down.

689
00:40:55,560 --> 00:40:57,160
My Lord, you shouldn't have asked me

690
00:40:57,160 --> 00:40:59,070
to communicate with the people of the Logistics Ministry.

691
00:40:59,070 --> 00:41:00,930
They're just a bunch of villains.

692
00:41:01,050 --> 00:41:01,920
What happened?

693
00:41:02,910 --> 00:41:04,060
Those several bastards

694
00:41:04,060 --> 00:41:05,630
didn't open the granary for us.

695
00:41:05,630 --> 00:41:07,870
They also said that they would ask their superiors to check us again.

696
00:41:07,870 --> 00:41:10,230
They said that our Xiu Battalion

697
00:41:10,390 --> 00:41:12,270
wasn't considered as a regular army,

698
00:41:12,270 --> 00:41:13,960
and our soldiers were just a bunch of ruffians and rascals.

699
00:41:13,960 --> 00:41:15,890
So you two came back empty-handed,

700
00:41:16,120 --> 00:41:18,070
and didn't bring any provisions back?

701
00:41:18,070 --> 00:41:21,280
I tried to use force to take some provisions, but in the end...

702
00:41:21,280 --> 00:41:23,630
In the end, Luo Jie failed to take anything away.

703
00:41:23,630 --> 00:41:25,430
He was even kicked twice by them.

704
00:41:27,390 --> 00:41:29,860
He was even kicked twice? Which part?

705
00:41:29,990 --> 00:41:31,710
My butt, but I'm fine.

706
00:41:31,730 --> 00:41:33,990
No, you're not fine.

707
00:41:33,990 --> 00:41:34,810
I'm really fine.

708
00:41:34,810 --> 00:41:35,120
I...

709
00:41:35,360 --> 00:41:36,090
I'm not fine.

710
00:41:36,380 --> 00:41:40,490
How dare they call us ruffians and rascals?

711
00:41:41,310 --> 00:41:43,240
What they said is right. Come here.

712
00:41:47,410 --> 00:41:49,610
Let's show them

713
00:41:49,830 --> 00:41:54,870
what real ruffians and rascals are like.
